languages.text: "Что, ледышка, переживаешь что и твои недобрые мыслишки подсмотрим? Не волнуйся, мы и так знаем, что тебе веры нет".
"What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

languages.text: «¿Qué pasa, hombre de hielo? ¿Le preocupa que acabemos viendo alguno de sus oscuros pensamientos? No debería. Ya sabemos que no es de fiar».
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

languages.text: 「どうしたの、氷の君？私たちが、あなたの心の闇を覗き見してないか心配？大丈夫よ。もう、あなたが信用できないことは知っているもの」
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

languages.text: “怎么了，冰人儿？你是担心我们可能会窥探到你那阴暗的思想吗？要是这样的话，就不用担心了，我们早就知道你这个人不能信。”
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

traits.locale_text: “怎么了，冰人儿？你是担心我们可能会窥探到你那阴暗的思想吗？要是这样的话，就不用担心了，我们早就知道你这个人不能信。”

languages.text: "Was ist, Eismann? Habt Ihr etwa Angst, wir könnten auch einen Blick in Eure dunklen Gedanken riskieren? Das müsst Ihr nicht. Wir wissen längst, dass wir Euch nicht trauen können."
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

languages.text: « Alors quoi, le rabat-joie ? Vous avez peur qu'on jette un coup d'œil dans vos propres pensées malsaines ? Inutile de vous inquiéter pour ça. On sait déjà que vous n'êtes pas digne de confiance. »
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."

languages.text: "Ne oldu buz küpü? Senin karanlık düşüncelerine de şöyle bir bakarız diye endişelendin mi yoksa? Hiç endişelenmene gerek yok. Sana güvenemeyeceğimizi zaten biliyoruz."
languages.original_text: "What is it, iceman? Are you worried we might take a peek inside your own dark thoughts? Well, don't be. We already know we can't trust you."
